\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{x}\sim\mathcal{N}\left(\boldsymbol{0},\boldsymbol{c}\right).
\end{equation}

\end_inset

In the following, we shall assume that process is specified by the matrix
